{"tid":782173,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"感情台不如改名叫假膠台","createTime":"2018-08-16T13:22:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-29T08:45:47.000Z","uid":172170,"like":20,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e16ff0373397cd9cb61f897ea98cdfc7d5f82214","tid":782173,"uid":172170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T13:22:35.000Z","msg":"首先請習慣睇內容前善用咗起底功能先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n每日睇啲熱門post<br />\n十個有八個都係啲假膠喺度作故仔<br />\n擺明扮港女臭雞搞分化嗰啲真係仆街嚟<br />\n慶幸依度都有好多明眼人提出嚟 我諗問題唔大<br />\n<br />\n最慘係有啲寫到幾慘幾真咁<br />\n追追下post先發現屌原來假嘅<br />\n當下感覺係我花咁多心機了解件事<br />\n留言安慰/解答樓主<br />\n點知原來俾人撚緊<br />\n唔好受㗎<br />\n咁樣完全係呃晒成班人嘅同情 為乜<br />\n<br />\n遲啲搞到啲真心開post嘅人冇人理<br />\n甚至如果有班人誤信 扭曲價值觀 咁點算<br />\n<br />\nBtw我都係認真撚中完伏想呻下啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e07dcf1aec514beb2e0b49de5b496c3941cefbb","tid":782173,"uid":138981,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T13:24:18.000Z","msg":"好多人睇唔出係假膠架重喺度狂鬧人臭雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n都唔知出啲假膠post有乜咁好玩"},{"pid":"e16108fa18ff050c1dab52a6301c5a897af7fdb8","tid":782173,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e07dcf1aec514beb2e0b49de5b496c3941cefbb","tid":782173,"uid":138981,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-16T13:24:18.000Z","msg":"好多人睇唔出係假膠架重喺度狂鬧人臭雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n都唔知出啲假膠post有乜咁好玩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T06:40:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"007b0ef1bb5a55cade4197affa936